{"tid":469070,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[初戀] 求指引 佢咁講咩意思","createTime":"2017-11-15T03:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-16T12:07:16.000Z","uid":33373,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"09936992d6ee0c348a63287a90dbd94c53c7c427","tid":469070,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:15:36.000Z","msg":"話說十月頭用交友apps識咗個女仔，幾日之後 交換whatsapp 之後約在出嚟&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n11.11( 第四次約會)睇完戲之後去睇燈飾之後就搵咗個公園坐下; 跟住瞓咗我膊頭我就勢拖佢&hellip;&hellip;之後個晚wts我話要講三個字同俾個身一份佢<br />\n<br />\n尋日佢第一日返新工， 接完放工之後搵咗個地方食嘢食完嘢之後去咗一個公園坐<br />\n<br />\n跟住開始講佢鍾意咩花( 藍色玫瑰、向日葵、繡球花&hellip;&hellip; )跟住又話 除咗拖手之外你見其他人仲做啲咩 快啲問下你啲朋友 同事請教下你咁唔得㗎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁啲同事知道我有拍拖之後問我尋日點， 我講完之後佢叫我唔好送住， 佢會唔會係娘娘收乒 問清楚之後先好送, 咁快要你送花 一定係 宣示主權, 仲要一起送埋咁貴嘅花<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry for  1999"},{"pid":"1e0d5e31d92559402dd2bce39b7b69d5b2875eb4","tid":469070,"uid":116289,"like":44,"dislike":1,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"嘻嘻嘻...雖然尋晚用左成份糧..不過ok la....拍拖緊係咁架啦...."},{"pid":"9edc6a059ca3741e9c0f65c5a331a2d2604742b7","tid":469070,"uid":122514,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"交友apps無真愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d71a06c0319816ba58c5a2589b893c960d3fe169","tid":469070,"uid":33373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:50:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4137aed113188bf5cb1cdd177bf9ca4eefcd061","tid":469070,"uid":157579,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"佢咪直接問 你願唔願意做我女朋友<br />\n加埋送花<br />\n花用得幾多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雙11 果下好sweet<img